enumerations.name: DiagnosticObdSupportEnum
enumerations.note: This meta-class represents the ability to model the roles in which a participation in OBD is foreseen. At the moment, this applies exclusively to the Dem. However, future extension of the Dcm may require this setting as well. Aggregated by DiagnosticEcuInstanceProps.obdSupport

literals.name: masterEcu
literals.description:
This represent the role "master ECU".
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: noObdSupport
literals.description:
This represents the ability to explicitly specify that no participation in OBD is foreseen.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1

literals.name: primaryEcu
literals.description:
This represents the role "primary ECU".
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=2

literals.name: secondaryEcu
literals.description:
This represents the role "secondary ECU".
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=3
